---



<img width="100%" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/OcEogMl0K3ibNBCibkF1cHwI5HwMtVHdDOEqMewqHtoItm6ibJZKJDuzZYNzvDHeKcfToqsjTX9xWseePE50wGicqQ/0">

<hr />
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16.363636016845703px;">
    <span style="color:#3f3f3f;">　　</span><span style="color:#3f3f3f;">这是Eric Whitacre的第一首作品。正是因为这个作品，Eric开始了他的职业作曲生涯。后来这个作品被收录在了《花之歌三首》中</span>
</p>
<hr />

<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16.363636016845703px;">
    <br />
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16.363636016845703px;text-align:center;">
    <strong><span style="font-size:20px;">Go, Lovely Rose</span></strong>
</p>

<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16.363636016845703px;text-align:center;">
    <span style="color:#7f7f7f;"><span style="color:#595959;">陈玮琦</span><br />
    </span>
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16.363636016845703px;text-align:center;">
    <span style="color:#595959;">人文爱乐合唱团女中音</span><br />
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16.363636016845703px;">
    <br />
</p>
<p>
    　　从春天的脚步开始慢慢融入泥土的瞬间，感受了土壤的包容和水的滋润，如人们期待般，一朵花的美丽奉献于自然。
</p>
<p>
    <br />
</p>
<p>
    　　初涉尘世的花朵迷茫般睁开了久违的双眼，静静的目睹晨起的朝阳，惊奇地感受每一滴雨露的问候，呼吸着空气里伴随着泥土的清香，沉浸在幸福的摇篮里唏嘘不已。
</p>
<p>
    <br />
</p>
<p>
    　　某一天晨曦，突然被发现慢慢疯长，一缕芬芳扑鼻而来，顷刻间，诱人的花蕾显露出最动人的妩媚，那丝娇艳不失华丽的做作，原来一朵花就这样自然的绽放在世俗的空间里。
</p>
<p>
    <br />
</p>
<p>
    　　岁月是否忘却了移动的脚步，依然徘徊在迷恋的季节。经过风雨的摧残，那花瓣失去了原有的光泽，渐渐的萎缩，直至无奈的凋谢，原来花如人的生命一样的脆弱和短暂。花开花落花自去，独留芬芳恋人间。
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16.363636016845703px;">
    <br />
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16.363636016845703px;">
    <strong>作曲家的话</strong>
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16.363636016845703px;">
    <br />
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16.363636016845703px;">
    　　这首曲子是根据玫瑰生命的周期所架构的，全曲都和一开始的玫瑰主题紧密结合，如同一粒种子般的从调性开始，并朝着各个方向生长，之后经历开花、枯萎，然后再次重生。每一个季节都被表现出来：曲子一开始的地方是春天，然后夏天从第13小节，秋天从第16小节，冬天从第39小节，最后从第49小节开始再回到了春天。整首曲子的黄金比例出现在第34小节当所有的声部再次结合起来组成一朵完全的花，就在最后的盛开以及无可避免的死亡和重生开始之前。每次的演唱都应该要带着如儿童般的纯洁及天真来处理，那才能使我们为了玫瑰在每个春天的重生感到惊奇。曲中所有的突强记号都应该处理得清亮且柔和。
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16.363636016845703px;">
    <br />
</p>
<hr style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16.363636016845703px;" />
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16.363636016845703px;">
    <br />
</p>
<p>
    <strong>Go, Lovely Rose</strong>
</p>
<p>
    <br />
</p>
<p>
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">Go, lovely rose</span>
</p>
<p>
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">Tell her that wastes her time and me,</span>
</p>
<p>
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">That now she knows,</span>
</p>
<p>
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">When I resemble her to thee,</span>
</p>
<p>
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">How sweet and fair she seems to be.</span>
</p>
<p>
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">Tell her that’s young,</span>
</p>
<p>
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">And shuns to have her graces spied,</span>
</p>
<p>
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">That hadst thou sprung</span>
</p>
<p>
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">In deserts where no men abide,</span>
</p>
<p>
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">Thou must have uncommended died.</span>
</p>
<p>
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">Small is the worth</span>
</p>
<p>
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">Of beauty from the light retired;</span>
</p>
<p>
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">Bid her come forth,</span>
</p>
<p>
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">Suffer herself to be desired,</span>
</p>
<p>
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">And not blush so to be admired.</span>
</p>
<p>
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">Then die! That she</span>
</p>
<p>
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">The common fate of all things rare</span>
</p>
<p>
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">May read in thee;</span>
</p>
<p>
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">How small a part of </span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">time they share,</span>
</p>
<p>
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">That are so wondrous sweet and fair!</span>
</p>
<p>
    <br />
</p>
<p>
    <span style="font-size:14px;">Edmund Waller, 1606-1687</span>
</p>
<p>
    <br />
</p>
<p>
    <br />
</p>
<hr style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16.363636016845703px;" />
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16.363636016845703px;">
    <span style="color:#3f3f3f;">　　<strong><a style="color:#3f3f3f;" href="http://t.cn/Rvo7vvx" target="_blank">点击这里</a></strong>，可以聆听由Polyphony带来的《Go, Lovely Rose》。这是《Cloudburst and Other Choral Works》这张专辑的第五首作品。</span>
</p>
<hr />
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16.363636016845703px;text-align:center;">
